        "payload": "node.web.summary",
        "title": "Declaration Demo",
        "purpose": "The declaration node is the authority/identity contract for a graph.\n\nEdit the declaration node and change:\n- identity (name/version)\n- dependencies (nodeTypes)\n- mutation policy (appendOnly)\n- surfaces (export allowlists)\n\nThen observe how the editor behaves (warnings, allowed edits).",
        "status": "active",
        "viewRole": "summary",
        "viewKind": "display",
        "exposedAuthority": "consume-view",
        "svg": "<svg viewBox=\"0 0 220 160\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" preserveAspectRatio=\"xMidYMid meet\"><rect x=\"18\" y=\"18\" width=\"184\" height=\"124\" rx=\"18\" fill=\"#ecfeff\" stroke=\"#0891b2\" stroke-width=\"5\"/><rect x=\"48\" y=\"44\" width=\"124\" height=\"72\" rx=\"14\" fill=\"#ffffff\" stroke=\"#67e8f9\" stroke-width=\"4\"/><path d=\"M62 64h96\" stroke=\"#111827\" stroke-width=\"10\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/><path d=\"M62 92h60\" stroke=\"#111827\" stroke-width=\"10\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" opacity=\"0.6\"/></svg>",
