    {
      "id": "declaration-demo-instructions",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Instructions",
      "position": {
        "x": 220,
        "y": 80
      },
      "width": 480,
      "height": 340,
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Try it\n\n1) Select the **Declaration** node and click **Edit**.\n2) Change `identity.name` and confirm it persists.\n3) Toggle `authority.mutation.appendOnly` and confirm it impacts edit affordances.\n4) Edit `declaration.surfaces[0].exposes.views.allowKeys` to see how allowlists are represented.\n\nThis is intentionally a pure contract editor demo."
      }
    }
